  <brief_title>Osteopathy in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Rehabilitation Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Osteopathic Treatment May Improve Exercise Capacity in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</official_title>
